descriptionHtml:
The TaxAssist app is just right for you! Perfect for Small Business and Self Employed Individuals who need the right service at the right time.

Our app has exciting features such as:
13 Tax Calculators!
Mileage Tracker
Tax Tables
News
Articles
Key Tax Dates
Tax Tips
Easy access to QuickBooks and Receipts Bank

We also have a special push notifications feature so that you never miss out on important updates.

Download the app today!

Disclaimer: Results and information provided by these calculators and content within the app is intended to inform rather than advise. Taxpayer's circumstances do vary and if you feel that the information provided is beneficial it is important that you contact us before implementation. If you take, or do not take action as a result of reading this, before receiving our written endorsement, we will accept no responsibility for any financial loss incurred.
